<td class="problemText" colspan="8" valign="middle" align="left">
            Public Class BinarySearchable<br>    Public Function howMany(ByVal sequence As Integer()) As Integer<br>        Dim i, j As Integer<br>        howMany = 0<br>        For i = 0 To sequence.Length - 1<br>            Dim found As Boolean = True<br>            For j = 0 To i - 1<br>                If sequence(j) &gt; sequence(i) Then<br>                    found = False<br>                    Exit For<br>                End If<br>            Next<br>            If found Then<br>                For j = i + 1 To sequence.Length - 1<br>                    If sequence(j) &lt; sequence(i) Then<br>                        found = False<br>                        Exit For<br>                    End If<br>                Next<br>            End If<br>            If found Then<br>                howMany += 1<br>            End If<br>        Next<br>    End Function<br>End Class<br></td>